#

Truffle Risotto with Wild Mushrooms and Asparagus

$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

MushroomsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodGourmet

Description

A creamy risotto infused with aromatic truffle oil, complemented by earthy wild mushrooms and fresh asparagus for a luxurious dining experience.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1 cup
  • Vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • Wild mushrooms (such as shiitake or oyster): 2 cups
  • Asparagus: 1 cup, chopped
  • Shallots: 1, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Parmesan cheese: ½ cup, grated
  • Truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh parsley: ¼ cup, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
